               <p>MR. PRICE. I am clerk of <placeName id="t18110403-94-crimeloc557">St. Dunstan Stepney</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18110403-94-crimeloc557" type="placeName" value="St. Dunstan Stepney"></interp>
